These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, grapes, pumpkin, watermelon
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, bike, airplane, helicopter
1. the person eating pumpkin is between the person driving the airplane and the person driving the bike##2
2. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
3. the person driving the airplane is not to the left of the person driving the airplane##8
4. the person driving the bike is not the person eating pumpkin##6
5. the person eating pumpkin is somewhere to the right of the person eating avocado##5
6. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | watermelon  | avocado | pumpkin | grapes  |
| Transport   | subway | airplane   | helicopter  | bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
House: colonial, townhouse, craftsman, futuristic
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, woodworking, card-games, singing
1. the person who's hobby is singing is not to the left of the person who's hobby is singing##8
2. the colonial house is somewhere to the right of the futuristic house##5
3. the colonial house is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the futuristic house is between the colonial house and the townhouse house##2
5. the townhouse house is somewhere between the craftsman house and the person who's hobby is camping##7
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the left of the townhouse house##5
7. the person who's hobby is camping is not to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| House   | craftsman | townhouse          | futuristic | colonial     |
| Hobby    | card-games      | singing | camping | woodworking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, rabbit, horse, frog
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, pop, disco, jazz
1. the fan of blues is not to the left of the owner of the horse##8
2. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is in an even position##4
5. the owner of the frog is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the fan of jazz##5
7. the owner of the frog is the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Pet           | goldfish | rabbit | horse     | frog |
| Music-Genre   | pop    | jazz   | blues | disco    |

