.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, swisher, ritmeester, montecristo
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk, fanta, sprite
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking milk is not to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##8
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
4. the montecristo-smoker is not to the right of the person drinking fanta##8
5. the alhambra-smoker is the person drinking milk##1
6. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
7. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the left of the montecristo-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Cigar   | ritmeester   | swisher         | montecristo   | alhambra    |
| Beverage         | soy-milk | sprite | fanta | milk |

