.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, train, van, motorbike
4 different pets are kept: dog, fish, snake, goldfish
1. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere between the person driving the skateboard and the person driving the train##7
2. the person driving the van is somewhere to the left of the owner of the snake##5
3. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere between the person driving the van and the person driving the skateboard##7
4. the person driving the van is not to the left of the owner of the goldfish##8
5. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the person driving the train and the owner of the fish##7
6. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the person driving the motorbike##5
7. the owner of the fish is not to the left of the person driving the skateboard##8
8. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Transport   | train   | van | motorbike | skateboard    |
| Pet         | dog | goldfish   | snake   | fish |

