.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, water, juice, cola
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, april, may, march
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
5. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
6. the person drinking cola is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##8
7. the person drinking cola is the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage          | cola | fanta | water  | juice |
| Birthday   | april   | march         | may | june |

