2. the person traveling to london is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in july and the person traveling to rome##7
3. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to nizza##5
4. the person traveling to london is not to the left of the person traveling to nizza##8
5. the person traveling to london is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##8
6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
7. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
8. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Birthday   | october      | may | january | july   |
| City      | nizza | rome | london  | hamburg |

