.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, november, may, february
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, mechanic, designer, dressmaker
1. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in february and the engineer##2
2. the dressmaker is on the far left##1
3. the dressmaker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
4. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the right of the engineer##5
5. the mechanic is the mechanic##1
6. the person who's birthday is in may is not the designer##6
7. the person who's birthday is in february is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##8
8. the engineer is not to the left of the mechanic##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Birthday   | february   | december | may | november |
| Job     | dressmaker | mechanic       | engineer  | designer    |

