.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, ice-hockey, cricket, lacrosse
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, october, july, march
1. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in march##8
2. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##8
3. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in july##2
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
7. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Sport    | ice-hockey        | lacrosse | cricket      | tennis    |
| Birthday   | january | july   | october | march |

