4. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person traveling to rome is somewhere between the person traveling to san-francisco and the person watching musical movies##7
7. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | musical         | action    | superhero       |
| City      | new-york | london | rome | san-francisco |

