.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-14::.
House: farmhouse, futuristic, victorian, gothic-revival
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, bridge, backgammon, chess
1. the person playing chess is not to the left of the person playing bridge##8
2. the gothic-revival house is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing chess is somewhere to the right of the gothic-revival house##5
4. the futuristic house is between the gothic-revival house and the person playing backgammon##2
5. the farmhouse house is on the far left##1
6. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person playing bridge and the person playing chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
| House   | farmhouse     | futuristic | gothic-revival        | victorian       |
| Game      | backgammon | bridge  | mah-jongg | chess |

