.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, r&b, trance, techno
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, azure, yellow, chestnut
 1. the person who likes chestnut is somewhere to the left of the person who likes yellow##5
 2. the fan of techno is not to the left of the fan of trance##8
 3. the fan of jazz is the person who likes yellow##1
 4. the person who likes yellow is not to the right of the person who likes azure##8
 5. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 6. the person who likes azure is somewhere to the right of the fan of trance##5
 7. the person who likes azure is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the fan of jazz is not to the right of the person who likes yellow##8
 9. the person who likes azure is not to the left of the fan of jazz##8
10. the fan of r&b is not to the left of the person who likes grey##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Music-Genre          | r&b    | trance | jazz | techno |
| Color   | grey | chestnut  | yellow     | azure    |

