.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, german, japanese, brazilian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, documentary, western, romance
1. the japanese is the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the japanese is not to the left of the person watching documentary movies##8
3. the person watching documentary movies is the person watching documentary movies##1
4. the person watching romance movies is the brazilian##1
5. the brazilian is on the left of the german##1
6. the german is between the person watching documentary movies and the brazilian##2
7. the japanese is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality    | brazilian        | german | spanish | japanese |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | western | documentary   | disaster    |

