1. the australian is not the librarian##6
2. the librarian is not to the right of the dutch##8
3. the mexican is somewhere between the dutch and the australian##7
4. the mechanic is somewhere to the right of the argentine##5
5. the mechanic is somewhere to the left of the paramedic##5
6. the journalist is not to the right of the mechanic##8
7. the mexican is not to the left of the paramedic##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality         | argentine  | australian | mexican  | dutch  |
| Job   | journalist | mechanic   | paramedic | librarian |

