.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, paramedic, designer, bartender
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, yellow, pink, azure
1. the person who likes yellow is not the engineer##6
2. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
3. the bartender is not to the left of the person who likes azure##8
4. the designer is the person who likes brown##1
5. the bartender is somewhere between the person who likes yellow and the person who likes brown##7
6. the bartender is on the left of the engineer##1
7. the person who likes pink is between the person who likes azure and the designer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Job         | paramedic    | bartender | engineer | designer |
| Color   | yellow | azure      | pink     | brown     |

 